{"tid":1417970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武唔代表唔需要冷靜","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:05:40.000Z","uid":105042,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2552e86aa9b046177c3f3606e0e756b731b9f98","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:41.000Z","msg":"話咗核彈都唔割，但我求下你地請檢討戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明火魔法應該hit and run，你班友就變咗camp fire，我極欣賞用大型彈弓做發射器，但火魔法方面你地真係要好好檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明知大家覺得火魔法唔可以隨便出，呢兩日就係咁出，出咗都算，但下下燒雜物，根本燒唔入肉，然後慢慢等到班狗清場，根本就變成你地單方面發泄，我地非勇武/和理非有顧及你地感受，你地又有冇？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班狗犯眾憎係因為醜態盡現，但你地都開始出現大量醜態</span></span><br />\n有人喺現場叫停勇武你又剩係話人左膠，你又有冇諗清楚先做每一個行動？黃大仙宿舍明明有其他紀律部隊，你仲走去玩火魔法?!然後又傳出示威者內控，都仲未計你地對街坊/影相人士嘅禮貌問題，搞到咁，有關公做公關都幫你唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本一班街坊零 gear去屌狗仲有力過你地，唔該你地檢討下，文宣手足都好辛苦，說好了各有各做，但唔好搞到我地跟唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗停，但要諗多步<br />\n唔洗改口號<br />\n勇武同冷靜無衝突<br />\n不要被仇恨支配自己<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"80d99cae578cf86ef9cdbbb2d0095ed849150144","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32e5ce7ededf2e200632927e764c126916238bac","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40fa2907b77af5fac796ea6ee6a0f3f2741171ef","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38a86e9a84ee1891d4a72ee2f1a245c5995892a4","tid":1417970,"uid":295400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"岩！前線真係要記住天琦講乜！"},{"pid":"5d831c15230dfa76cd8cb69a2779462c8ed08769","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"48a9d54e7c4974e9f87b39c3ae479aa29df69ceb","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"我唔想再見到前線同中後排內控，兩邊一齊檢討，OK?"},{"pid":"32de88f38627ef394f7e5dfe8082459667e52fd7","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:57.000Z","msg":"我唔想再見到前線同中後排內控，兩邊一齊檢討，OK?"},{"pid":"8e82adc1b4bff71938c01fcc4f4f1b34aa404d0e","tid":1417970,"uid":271431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"燒狗門口 然後整D爆炸野出黎 好有視覺效果<br />\n記者同7婆肯定好中意依種場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f54dafadd1e3ca433947ef9fc9c636447123799","tid":1417970,"uid":80905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:57:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b416170cdab08aacc0521c3e1dbf9300a0433e2","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔見火光/爆炸，你扔磚都開始有人唔理你，但一見火光，要出消防，大家就好易不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3e1d3bcc25f96bd3354bf9ee48c6c4491babd4","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔聽我講，可以聽梁天琦講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難當中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」 梁天琦"},{"pid":"a5074e16517e34107371631434a6dd2f57936555","tid":1417970,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT